title: [Solhaven, Dark Tree]
description: The branches of the ancient black willow tree twist about themselves, offering numerous locations throughout for comfortable seating.  Graceful black leaflets attached to long dark green stems shimmer a shadowy black as they rustle against the rough bark of the tree.  A faint rattling sound can be heard emanating from within the core of the tree.

The branches of the ancient black willow tree twist about themselves, offering numerous locations throughout for comfortable seating.  Graceful black leaflets attached to long dark green stems rustle against the bark of the tree, and a very fine pollen lingers in the air about you.
